OL,7,F"We need to be very careful for his
OL,8,Fmental wellbeing and also his
OL,9,Feducation."
OL,11,FAdrian was one of a group of Parents
OL,12,Fwho met with MLA's at Stormont
OL,13,Frecently to plead their case for their
OL,14,Fchildren.
OL,16,FEmmett's mum like all the others, is
OL,17,Fworried that he would be out of his
OL,18,Fdepth in a mainstream school.
OL,20,F"He would be about 5 or 6 years behind
OL,21,Fjust due to when he got implanted"
