OL,5,CAuthority
OL,7,FThere are thousands of vulnerable
OL,8,Fchildren like Emmett in the same
OL,9,Fsituation
OL,11,FTheir parents feel completely let down
OL,12,Fby the Education Authority.
OL,14,F"A lot of the parents that we are
OL,15,Fdealing with as a group are saying
OL,16,Ftheir children need specialist help,
OL,17,Fthat they are not coping in units and
OL,18,Fthey won't cope in mainstream
OL,19,Fsecondary schools."
